{"arkId":"cl010056523","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010056523","modified ":"2026-03-11","title":"Arabesques. Un sacrifice","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Arabesques. Un sacrifice"}],"displayDateCreated":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : XVIIe si\u00e8cle (1600 - 1700 et 1693)","currentLocation":"Fontainebleau (France), Mus\u00e9e national du ch\u00e2teau de Fontainebleau","room":"","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1600,"endYear":1700,"imprecision":"","text":"XVIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""},{"startYear":1693,"endYear":"","imprecision":"","text":"","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Coypel, No\u00ebl","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","dates":[{"date":"1707","place":"Paris","type":"date de mort"},{"date":"1628","place":"Paris","type":"date de naissance"}],"creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q975135"},{"label":"France","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"\u00c9cole de","creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"INV 8973","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"},{"value":"B 1732","type":"Autre num\u00e9ro d\u0027inventaire"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Peintures","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Triomphe de V\u00e9nus, carton de tapisserie de la tenture des Triomphes des Dieux","inscriptions":"","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"5","displayDimension":"5 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"1","displayDimension":"1 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"toile","placeOfCreation":"","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Ce num\u00e9ro d\u0027inventaire pourrait correspondre au carton de tapisserie de No\u00ebl Coypel en 7 bandes d\u00e9pos\u00e9 au ch\u00e2teau de Fontainebleau en 1939. Dans l\u0027inventaire B, au num\u00e9ro 1732 est cit\u00e9 un carton des Arabesques avec au crayon une description d\u00e9taill\u00e9e, soit le Triomphe de V\u00e9nus en 7 bandes, jug\u00e9 complet, le Triomphe de C\u00e9r\u00e8s en 1 bande et le Triomphe de Saturne en 1 bande, ces deux derniers jug\u00e9s incomplets. Ces 9 bandes sont inventori\u00e9es ensuite sous le n\u00b0 MR 4268. Il semble que le Triomphe de C\u00e9r\u00e8s ait \u00e9t\u00e9 inventori\u00e9 ensuite par Villot sous le n\u00b0 INV. 3492 et le Triomphe de Saturne sous le n\u00b0 INV. 3495. En revanche, aucune description de l\u0027inventaire Villot ne cite clairement un Triomphe de V\u00e9nus. Par recoupement, il pourrait s\u0027agir du INV. 8973 : le Triomphe de V\u00e9nus conserv\u00e9 \u00e0 Fontainebleau pr\u00e9sente en effet deux sc\u00e8nes pouvant s\u0027apparenter \u00e0 un sacrifice.","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"ancienne collection","doubt":"","dates":[]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Peintures","longTermLoanTo":"Mus\u00e9e national du ch\u00e2teau de Fontainebleau, Fontainebleau","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"ancienne collection"}]},"bibliography":[{"bibliographyRef":"No\u00ebl Coypel (1628-1707), Peintre du roi, sous la dir. de Guillaume Kazerouni et B\u00e9atrice Sarrazin, cat. exp. mus\u00e9e national des ch\u00e2teaux de Versailles (26\/09\/2023 au 28\/01\/2024) et mus\u00e9e des Beaux-Arts de Rennes (17\/02\/2024 au 05\/05\/2024), Gand, \u00c9ditions Snoeck, 2023.","bibliographyDate":"2023","bibliographyDetail":"p. 168-277, 278-279, ill. en coul., Cat. 131","comparison":false},{"bibliographyRef":"Bertrand, Pascal-Fran\u00e7ois, La peinture tiss\u00e9e: th\u00e9orie de l\u0027art et tapisseries des Gobelins sous Louis XIV, Rennes, Presses universitaires de Rennes, 2015","bibliographyDate":"2015","bibliographyDetail":"p. 35, 37, 130, Fig. 23 (coul.)","comparison":false}],"exhibition":[{"value":"No\u00ebl Coypel et le Grand D\u00e9cor, Versailles (Externe, France), Ch\u00e2teau - Domaine national de Versailles, 26\/09\/2023 - 28\/01\/2024, \u00e9tape d\u0027une exposition itin\u00e9rante "}],"relatedWork":[],"image":[{"urlImage":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/large\/0000000021\/0000056523\/0000924014_OG.JPG","urlThumbnail":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/small\/0000000021\/0000056523\/0000924014_OG.JPG","copyright":"\u00a9 2011 GrandPalaisRmn (mus\u00e9e du Louvre) \/ Michel Urtado","type":"face, recto, avers, avant ; vue d\u0027ensemble ; vue sans cadre","position":0},{"urlImage":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/large\/0000000021\/0000056523\/0000372225_OG.JPG","urlThumbnail":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/small\/0000000021\/0000056523\/0000372225_OG.JPG","copyright":"\u00a9 2015 Mus\u00e9e du Louvre \/ D\u00e9partement des Peintures","type":"","position":1},{"urlImage":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/large\/0000000021\/0000056523\/0000924016_OG.JPG","urlThumbnail":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/small\/0000000021\/0000056523\/0000924016_OG.JPG","copyright":"\u00a9 2011 GrandPalaisRmn (mus\u00e9e du Louvre) \/ Michel Urtado","type":"face, recto, avers, avant ; d\u00e9tail","position":2},{"urlImage":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/large\/0000000021\/0000056523\/0000924018_OG.JPG","urlThumbnail":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/small\/0000000021\/0000056523\/0000924018_OG.JPG","copyright":"\u00a9 2011 GrandPalaisRmn (mus\u00e9e du Louvre) \/ Michel Urtado","type":"face, recto,